		<content>{A MUSLIM}follows the religion of Islam
 which means "to submit" There are 5   
 mosques in Halifax.A mosque is a place
 where Muslims go to pray and read the 
 Koran.Mohammed is the prophet of      
 Islam.                                
{ There are 5 pillars of Islam-        
   Pray 5 times a day                  
   Read the Koran                      
  Visit Mecca at least once in a life  
   Pay alms to the poor and the Mosque 
   Live in peace                       
 Friday is the holiest day of the week 
 and the holiest month is Ramadan,when 
 Muslims fast during the hours of      
 daylight.It lasts 29 days.            
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
